data.description: Discover serenity in this move-in ready 3b/2b home, nestled in a peaceful neighborhood. The split floorplan ensures privacy, while the open living room and bright kitchen create a welcoming atmosphere. Enjoy outdoor living on the screened-in patio overlooking the fenced backyard. The kitchen effortlessly connects to the dining area. The owner's suite features a step-in shower, providing convenience. Two versatile rooms cater to your needs, be it bedrooms, an office, or more. Enjoy comfort and convenience with a 2-car garage and proximity to shopping and I-95. This home effortlessly combines comfort and ease! 7 year old roof
